modName: Sam The tough Ashen Save Game
summary: Want to have a new start? Tired of making characters? Try this out!
descriptionHtml:
This is a save game of a Ashen Female. This save is fresh, so the only thing that was completed was leaving helgen. Also the player is joined with the stormcloaks. This charcter was made while having the CBBE Body type on a side note. 

The Eyes I am 95% sure are from the lovergirl race, Besides that you will be good-to-go.

Instal
-Open Zip, and copy/drag the save game into your saves folder. Usually in Documents-My games-Skyrim-Saves 
Want to see some of my videos? Follow this link: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Ma8XBSAPk0
If you want me to make a video of something Skyrim Related, pm me!

Credit/Requirements
